ien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/author-h3EvqeQvlQUxq2sceUWWYQ">Đoàn Huyên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/T%E1%BB%91ng-kh%C3%A2m-ph%C3%A1i-%C4%91%E1%BB%91c-bi%E1%BB%87n-H%C6%B0ng-Y%C3%AAn-th%C3%A0nh-c%C3%B4ng-C%E1%BB%ADu-Y%C3%AAn-h%C3%A0-c%C3%B4ng-c%C3%B4ng-b%E1%BB%99-lang-trung-L%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-h%E1%BB%93i-kinh/poem-fcLtFsn8sd0mAkNiaIL1Uw">Tống khâm phái đốc biện Hưng Yên thành công Cửu Yên hà công công bộ lang trung Lương hồi kinh - 送欽派督辨興安城工久安河工工部郎中梁回京</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/author-h3EvqeQvlQUxq2sceUWWYQ">Đoàn Huyên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-V%C4%A9-Nghi%E1%BB%87p/Uy%C3%AAn-h%E1%BB%93-kh%C3%BAc/poem-aw_k9y8xFFL9IBn8k3lN1A">Uyên hồ khúc - 鴛湖曲</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-V%C4%A9-Nghi%E1%BB%87p/author-clxY5GFWegDsEw0Y8VPiNQ">Ngô Vĩ Nghiệp</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-s%E1%BB%AD-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-V8R7nhhotOVWLkm8vPg4Jg">Vịnh sử kỳ 1 - 詠史其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/author-9iJ5oLtFQBkuT0Ej5xvn9Q">Lý Thương Ẩn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/Xu%C3%A2n-m%E1%BB%99/poem-_dMOlzb-UpEIjw8m8dm81Q">Xuân mộ - 春暮</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br></div>	</div>
